# Group MetaTags
MetaTags can be accessed here, and admins can update / add new ones. 
MetaTags can have sub-metaTags, they can be accessed via `metaTags` on a MetaTag object. There is currently only 2 levels of metaTags allowed. 
`parent` is either null or the metaTag that the current metaTag is a sub-metaTag of.


## MetaTags Collection [/metaTags?include=includes&limit=limit]
+ Parameters
    + limit (optional, number, `1`) ... Numerical `limit` to apply to how many records are returned.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `metaTags`,`parent` or `all`

